01:34:22,391 --> 01:34:23,151
[SPEAKER_04]: Thank you very much.

584
01:34:23,431 --> 01:34:24,212
[SPEAKER_04]: Thank you for having me.

585
01:34:25,312 --> 01:34:26,973
[SPEAKER_04]: Mother to Son by Langston Hughes.

586
01:34:28,339 --> 01:34:33,924
[SPEAKER_04]: Well, son, I'll tell you, life for me ain't been no crystal stair.

587
01:34:34,725 --> 01:34:43,152
