588
01:34:44,013 --> 01:34:52,620
[SPEAKER_04]: But all the time I've been climbing on, and reaching landings, and turning corners, and sometimes going in the dark where there ain't been no light.

589
01:34:53,661 --> 01:34:55,523
[SPEAKER_04]: So, boy, don't you turn back.

590
01:34:57,037 --> 01:35:00,242
[SPEAKER_04]: Don't you set down on the steps, because you'll find it's kind of hard.

591
01:35:00,903 --> 01:35:03,367
