592
01:35:03,648 --> 01:35:04,529
[SPEAKER_04]: I'm still climbing.

593
01:35:05,270 --> 01:35:07,955
[SPEAKER_04]: And life for me ain't been no crystal stair.

594
01:35:17,048 --> 01:35:31,547
