01:35:50,703 --> 01:35:58,648
[SPEAKER_04]: And there'll be two moments where it'll seem obvious that I'm gonna try to get you to say don't quit with me, and I'll probably point at you just like a teacher.

598
01:36:00,780 --> 01:36:06,963
[SPEAKER_04]: Well, my student, my charge, I've seen you struggling with the world you've inherited.

599
01:36:07,683 --> 01:36:29,132
[SPEAKER_04]: I've seen you trying to find your balance on this shaky ground, trying to swim, drowning in screens, trying to walk with ice on our streets, trying to assert yourself, facing the danger in being who you are, trying to be independent with the expectation of servility and conformity,

600
01:36:29,852 --> 01:36:35,014
[SPEAKER_04]: the greed and damage of a system that is built to keep you powerless and disenfranchised.

601
01:36:36,135 --> 01:36:44,819
[SPEAKER_04]: So it is tempting to recede in the shadows, to let others do the work, to wait for someone to stand up for you.

602
01:36:45,859 --> 01:36:49,981
[SPEAKER_04]: And while you're young, you can do it a little bit.

603
01:36:51,102 --> 01:36:51,742
[SPEAKER_04]: But don't quit.

604
01:36:53,443 --> 01:36:54,344
[SPEAKER_04]: Say it with me now.

605
01:36:55,125 --> 01:36:55,946
[SPEAKER_04]: Don't quit.

606
01:36:57,168 --> 01:37:06,819
[SPEAKER_04]: As much as the only life you get to live needs you to be that bravery, we need you to be that bravery.

607
01:37:07,660 --> 01:37:09,322
[SPEAKER_04]: When we see someone stand up,

608
01:37:10,163 --> 01:37:10,944
[SPEAKER_04]: We stand up.

609
01:37:11,625 --> 01:37:17,390
[SPEAKER_04]: When we hear someone raise their voice in the service of others, we dare to as well.

610
01:37:18,291 --> 01:37:26,939
[SPEAKER_04]: The country that needs to awaken and remember its identity and its promise to be a human family needs you.

611
01:37:28,080 --> 01:37:29,742
[SPEAKER_04]: Each struggle is different.

612
01:37:30,363 --> 01:37:34,585
[SPEAKER_04]: Yeah, each struggle is real, but I am here for you.

613
01:37:35,405 --> 01:37:36,786
[SPEAKER_04]: We are here for you.

614
01:37:37,466 --> 01:37:39,387
[SPEAKER_04]: We will be your support beams.

615
01:37:40,308 --> 01:37:41,028
[SPEAKER_04]: So don't quit.

616
01:37:42,208 --> 01:37:44,750
[SPEAKER_04]: I've got you, and I'm sure you've got me.

617
01:37:45,450 --> 01:37:46,350
[SPEAKER_04]: Trust me on this.

618
01:37:47,111 --> 01:37:47,651
[SPEAKER_04]: Don't quit.

619
01:37:48,731 --> 01:37:49,552
[SPEAKER_04]: Say it with me now.

620
01:37:49,572 --> 01:37:51,513
[SPEAKER_04]: Don't quit.

621
01:37:51,973 --> 01:37:52,293
[SPEAKER_04]: Thank you.

