[SPEAKER_13]: We shall live in peace.

848
02:06:09,065 --> 02:06:36,372
[SPEAKER_13]: Someday, oh, deep in my heart, I do believe we shall live in peace one day.

849
02:06:36,492 --> 02:06:37,692
[SPEAKER_13]: One more time, one more thing.

850
02:06:38,511 --> 02:06:42,475
[SPEAKER_13]: We are not afraid.

851
02:06:42,715 --> 02:06:43,796
[SPEAKER_13]: We're not afraid.

852
02:06:44,436 --> 02:06:47,939
[SPEAKER_13]: We are not afraid.

853
02:06:47,979 --> 02:06:48,960
[SPEAKER_13]: You believe it, right?

854
02:06:49,521 --> 02:06:50,481
[SPEAKER_13]: We are not afraid.

855
02:06:50,642 --> 02:06:54,785
[SPEAKER_13]: We are not afraid today.

856
02:06:54,805 --> 02:06:55,266
[SPEAKER_13]: Today.

857
02:07:00,069 --> 02:07:19,961
[SPEAKER_13]: Oh, so deep in my heart, I do believe we will overcome, that we shall overcome someday.

858
