[SPEAKER_13]: Yes.

859
02:07:26,941 --> 02:07:27,501
[SPEAKER_13]: Thank you.

860
02:07:30,004 --> 02:07:32,226
[SPEAKER_13]: Give yourselves a big hand, big hand.

861
02:07:32,647 --> 02:07:36,050
[SPEAKER_13]: We shall overcome today.

