02:07:41,396 --> 02:07:41,956
[SPEAKER_11]: Thank you.

867
02:07:42,377 --> 02:07:44,179
[SPEAKER_11]: Thank you, Athene, so much.

868
02:07:48,222 --> 02:07:51,604
[SPEAKER_11]: OK, like I said, friends and allies.

869
02:07:53,025 --> 02:07:59,208
[SPEAKER_11]: And from one important tradition to the next, I would like to bring another friend front and center.

870
02:08:00,028 --> 02:08:15,336
[SPEAKER_11]: Jill Harvey is the chief equity officer of the Mass Municipal Association and previously served as the inaugural director of diversity, equity, and inclusion in the Division of Health and Human Services for the town of Arlington.

871
