[SPEAKER_11]: She is both persistent and determined to make a difference.

878
02:08:59,886 --> 02:09:11,215
[SPEAKER_11]: And we've asked her to deliver our charge as we leave this gathering to continue on in this kindred journey to active commitment in Medford and beyond.

